# Privacy Policy – Annam

Last Updated: June 2026

Welcome to Annam. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information.

## Information We Collect

The application may collect and store the following information:

* Account information such as name, email address, and phone number.
* Farm information and livestock records entered by users.
* Animal data, including health records, vaccinations, births, production, and related information.
* Location data (only when permission is granted and required for app features such as weather information).
* Device information required for notifications and application functionality.

## How We Use Information

We use the collected information to:

* Provide and improve application services.
* Manage farms, livestock, health records, and related activities.
* Send notifications and reminders requested by the user.
* Provide technical support and customer service.
* Improve application performance and user experience.

## Data Storage and Security

We take reasonable measures to protect user information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.

Data may be stored securely using cloud services and local device storage to support application functionality.

## Third-Party Services

The application may use third-party services including:

* Firebase Authentication
* Firebase Firestore
* Firebase Cloud Messaging
* Weather data providers
* Apple Sign In
* Google Sign In
* Google Maps services (if enabled)

These services may process information according to their own privacy policies.

## User-Generated Content

Users are responsible for the information they create and manage within the application, including farm records, livestock information, and communications.

## Notifications

The application may send notifications related to:

* Livestock management
* Vaccinations
* Treatments
* Birth records
* Reminders
* Support messages
* Veterinary communications

Users can manage notification permissions through their device settings.

## Children's Privacy

The application is not specifically directed toward children under the age required by applicable laws.

## Data Deletion

Users may request deletion of their account and associated data through the application or by contacting support.

## Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will become effective when published within the application or related services.

